net.codemusic.smartears.event
Class EventManager

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--net.codemusic.smartears.event.EventManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
IExampleEventManager, IExcerciseEventManager, IScoreEventManager, ISettingsEventManager
public class EventManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements IExampleEventManager, IScoreEventManager, ISettingsEventManager, IExcerciseEventManager

This class handles registering, unregistering, and notifying all of the model-related event listeners in the SmartEars system. The Managers should begin event propogation by calling the appropriate processXXX() method in this class. The methods are self-explainatory.
